{
  "id": "604646f6f5f0d8001fa77ea1",
  "title": "認知の歪み",
  "created": 1615218434,
  "updated": 1628527056,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "604646f6f5f0d8001fa77ea1",
      "text": "認知の歪み",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1615218434,
      "updated": 1615218434
    },
    {
      "id": "61115956aff09e0000c81ff4",
      "text": "[認知の機能不良], [認知の狂い]などの言葉を使って来たが2021年現在「認知の歪み」という表現がメジャーか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1628526934,
      "updated": 1628527012
    },
    {
      "id": "611159a4aff09e0000aa4166",
      "text": "　下記の具体的なリストのことではなく、良くない認知パターンや、[人間のバグ]を指して使っている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1628527012,
      "updated": 1628527056
    },
    {
      "id": "611159a4aff09e0000aa4167",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1628527012,
      "updated": 1628527012
    },
    {
      "id": "61115956aff09e0000c81ff5",
      "text": "-----",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1628526934,
      "updated": 1628526938
    },
    {
      "id": "60464724aff09e000078ac6d",
      "text": "[非合理的な思考パターン] [人間のバグ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1615218469,
      "updated": 1615218490
    },
    {
      "id": "60464703aff09e000078ac6b",
      "text": ">この概念は精神科医アーロン・ベックが基礎を築き、彼の弟子のデビッド・Ｄ・バーンズ（英語版）がその研究を引き継いだ。最も有名なのはバーンズが1989年に著した『フィーリングGoodハンドブック』であり、これらの認知パターンを学び、かつ除去する方法を記している。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1615218435,
      "updated": 1615218458
    },
    {
      "id": "60464715aff09e000078ac6c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1615218453,
      "updated": 1615218453
    },
    {
      "id": "6046475daff09e000078ac6e",
      "text": " [全か無かの思考]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1615218525,
      "updated": 1615218599
    },
    {
      "id": "6046475daff09e000078ac6f",
      "text": " [行き過ぎた一般化]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1615218525,
      "updated": 1615218599
    },
    {
      "id": "6046475daff09e000078ac70",
      "text": " [心のフィルター]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1615218525,
      "updated": 1615218599
    },
    {
      "id": "604647c0aff09e000078ac79",
      "text": " \t[選択的抽象化]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1615218625,
      "updated": 1615218662
    },
    {
      "id": "604647e6aff09e0000c21146",
      "text": " \t悪いところに注目する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1615218662,
      "updated": 1615218668
    },
    {
      "id": "6046475daff09e000078ac71",
      "text": " [マイナス化思考]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1615218525,
      "updated": 1615218682
    },
    {
      "id": "6046486baff09e000078ac7e",
      "text": " \t上手くいったら「これはまぐれだ」と思い、上手くいかなかったら「やっぱりそうなんだ」と考える",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1615218796,
      "updated": 1615218796
    },
    {
      "id": "6046475daff09e000078ac72",
      "text": " [論理の飛躍]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1615218525,
      "updated": 1615218599
    },
    {
      "id": "60464810aff09e000078ac7a",
      "text": " \t[心の読みすぎ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1615218705,
      "updated": 1615218706
    },
    {
      "id": "60464814aff09e000078ac7b",
      "text": " \t[先読みの誤り]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1615218709,
      "updated": 1615218717
    },
    {
      "id": "6046475daff09e000078ac73",
      "text": " [拡大解釈]、[過小解釈]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1615218525,
      "updated": 1615218599
    },
    {
      "id": "6046475daff09e000078ac74",
      "text": " [感情の理由づけ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1615218525,
      "updated": 1615218599
    },
    {
      "id": "60464831aff09e000078ac7c",
      "text": " \t感情のみを根拠として、自分の考えが正しいと結論を下す",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1615218737,
      "updated": 1615218738
    },
    {
      "id": "6046475daff09e000078ac75",
      "text": " [～すべき思考]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1615218525,
      "updated": 1615218599
    },
    {
      "id": "604647a8aff09e000078ac78",
      "text": " \t[世界を現実と違った形に期待している]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1615218601,
      "updated": 1615218601
    },
    {
      "id": "6046475daff09e000078ac76",
      "text": " [レッテル貼り]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1615218525,
      "updated": 1615218599
    },
    {
      "id": "6046475daff09e000078ac77",
      "text": " [誤った自己責任化]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1615218525,
      "updated": 1615218599
    }
  ]
}